      <title>木星的大红斑可能已经消失并重新形成</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2436530-jupiters-great-red-spot-may-have-disappeared-and-reformed/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
